data.description: Welcome to 3683 Persimmon Park Drive in Wesley Chapel! You're going to love this 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom smart home with an office/den and 2 car garage! This is a David Weekley Homes Belmeade design featuring tons of options. Let's dig in! As you approach the home you'll notice the welcoming front porch with pavers - perfect for relaxing in a rocking chair and enjoying the Florida sunshine! You'll also notice there is a fitness trail that borders the property. This is a terrific feature that dramatically increases the space between the neighboring property! Inside you're going to love the tasteful choice of upgrades the sellers have chosen. Once inside you'll find the office/den featuring french doors, and you'll notice the upgraded carpet that is also in all the bedrooms. The rest of the living space features beautiful luxury vinyl plank flooring. When you enter the kitchen you'll love the oversized island, upgraded built-in oven, cook-top, and designer range hood! The kitchen and bathrooms also feature quartz countertops. In the large primary bedroom, be sure to check out the tray ceiling and en-suite bathroom. In the primary bathroom you'll notice the upgraded "super shower" and walk-in closet giving you a luxurious spa-like feel. This home also features a covered and screened in lanai and breezeway with pavers connecting you to the 2 car garage. This lanai is sure to be your go-to spot for hosting guests, or just enjoying the outdoors (bug-free)! The garage entrance is accessed from the alley behind the house, giving you an extra measure of privacy! This smart home also features security cameras, smart switches, and upgraded internet capabilities. Persimmon Park is conveniently located in the heart of Wesley Chapel, with easy access to shopping, dining, and medical facilities. If there is a restaurant or store that you want, and it isn't here, I'll bet it's in the works! Persimmon Park also features a number of community amenities and benefits such as reclaimed water for irrigation, cable and internet included in HOA fees, a swimming pool, dog park, and playground! Schedule your private tour today!
